## 🚀 Installation

### Clone the Repository

```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/diet_ai_project.git
```

### Navigate to the Project Folder

```bash
cd diet_ai_project
```

### Install Dependencies

```bash
pip install flask pandas scikit-learn matplotlib
```

### Run the Application

```bash
python app.py
```

### Open in Browser

```
http://127.0.0.1:5000
```

